INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2012-07-02 04:46:11','2012-07-02 04:46:11','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2012-07-08 17:46:31','2012-07-09 00:46:31','',0,'http://sd-trunk/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2012-07-02 04:46:11','2012-07-02 04:46:11','<h3>The Early Years...</h3>\r\n<p>Alan’s business acumen began to develop from the age of 16 years when his father purchased his first business for him. His passion for business continued to grow and launched him successfully into the world of Professional and Personal Development at age 22. By the time Alan was 26 he had become an International company’s Training Facilitator for Australia, USA and Asia. In 1988 Alan at 30 years of age began his own International consulting and training company.</p>\r\n<h3>Longevity...</h3>\r\n<p>With a broad and successful background in business spanning 37 years, Alan has competently brought skilled implementation of strategies, practical facilitation techniques and advanced training programs to companies across the world. His obvious and long term experience in the business world, together with his professional level of skill, command respect and attention from corporations and place Alan’s services in high demand.</p>\r\n<h3>Business Values...</h3>\r\n<p>An uncompromising application of sound business principles and inspirational ideas combined with \'old fashion values\' has earned Alan a reputation for business excellence with integrity. Alan\'s life is dedicated to bringing significant improvement to companies and their staff. His unique \'people skill\' ability and advanced training techniques allows Alan to implement \'change for gain\'... resulting in long term measurable and significant profitability. Alan is passionately committed to delivering excellence in all areas of business life.</p>\r\n<h3>Strengths...</h3>\r\n<p>Alan is a gifted strategist, facilitator, platform speaker, educator and trainer who provides a diversity of customized services to fit the need of a company, small business or large corporation. Alan identifies, designs and implements a unique program for each company client and then competently and intentionally delivers the program... with Quantum results...!</p>','Alan Strudwick','','publish','open','open','','founder','','','2012-07-14 16:11:58','2012-07-14 23:11:58','',0,'http://sd-trunk/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(6,1,'2012-07-14 15:54:36','2012-07-14 22:54:36','<h3>The Early Years...</h3>\nAlan’s business acumen began to develop from the age of 16 years when his father purchased his first business for him. His passion for business continued to grow and launched him successfully into the world of Professional and Personal Development at age 22. By the time Alan was 26 he had become an International company’s Training Facilitator for Australia, USA and Asia. In 1988 Alan at 30 years of age began his own International consulting and training company.\n<h3>Longevity...</h3>\nWith a broad and successful background in business spanning 37 years, Alan has competently brought skilled implementation of strategies, practical facilitation techniques and advanced training programs to companies across the world. His obvious and long term experience in the business world, together with his professional level of skill, command respect and attention from corporations and place Alan’s services in high demand.\n<h3>Business Values...</h3>\nAn uncompromising application of sound business principles and inspirational ideas combined with \'old fashion values\' has earned Alan a reputation for business excellence with integrity. Alan\'s life is dedicated to bringing significant improvement to companies and their staff. His unique \'people skill\' ability and advanced training techniques allows Alan to implement \'change for gain\'... resulting in long term measurable and significant profitability. Alan is passionately committed to delivering excellence in all areas of business life.\n<h3>Strengths...</h3>\nAlan is a gifted strategist, facilitator, platform speaker, educator and trainer who provides a diversity of customized services to fit the need of a company, small business or large corporation. Alan identifies, designs and implements a unique program for each company client and then competently and intentionally delivers the program... with Quantum results...!','Alan Strudwick','','inherit','open','open','','2-autosave','','','2012-07-14 15:54:36','2012-07-14 22:54:36','',2,'http://sd-trunk/2-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(7,1,'2012-07-02 04:46:11','2012-07-02 04:46:11','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickies to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://sd-trunk/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision','','','2012-07-02 04:46:11','2012-07-02 04:46:11','',2,'http://sd-trunk/2-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(8,1,'2012-07-08 13:26:54','2012-07-08 20:26:54','','Services','Services','publish','open','open','','categories','','','2012-07-14 14:09:42','2012-07-14 21:09:42','',0,'http://sd-trunk/?p=8',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(9,1,'2012-07-08 14:20:54','2012-07-08 21:20:54','<blockquote>\r\n<p>\"Creative Holidays\' success over the last 6 years is in no small way due to the close relationship that we have with Alan. In our earlier years of growth, the Change Program developed for us gave us the cohesion and focus that we needed to forge ahead. As we grew, our Management Team Skills were also enhanced by Presentation and Communication Training coupled with Extensive Development time spent with supervisors through Sales Management training throughout our company. As our team became better communicators, better trainers, better presenters & better sales people, then Creative grew.</p>\r\n<p>The close association between our companies over that extended period has provided Alan with the insight into our unique culture,  that allows him to customise training to perfectly suit the needs of each of our staff members. This ongoing intimacy with the culture that is so important to us, ensures all the trainings he provides are accepted with a high level of confidence. We can be sure that our company\'s needs are being met in every way. More importantly, Alan, is well liked by our people, well respected, and has formed an ongoing part of our company\'s personal and commercial development and is a part of our amazing success story.\"</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h4>Creative Holidays</h4>\r\n<div class=\"video\">\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/themes/sd/assets/img/video-placeholder.png\" />\r\n</div>\r\n<blockquote>\"The Consulting Program has had a positive impact on my personal development, especially in the area of identifying areas of potential weaknesses. Having identified these and working to correct them has helped me no end in a Team and Management environment.\"\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h4>Peters Ice Cream</h4>\r\n<blockquote>\"Alan\'s approach to training our team, I feel, has been remarkable. He really does know how to read people, understands our fears, encourages us and knows how to make us work to the best of our abilities to achieve the best results.\"</blockquote>\r\n<h4>Managing Director - Legion Interactive</h4>\r\n<blockquote>\"Alan Strudwick has the key quality that we look for in our pilots, that is...The Edge\"</blockquote>\r\n<h4>Qantas</h4>\r\n<blockquote>\"The things that I\'ve learned from the program have not only helped me with work but also to make a better approach to the day to day living as well. I appreciate the dedication that you have input into every session, I\'ve enjoyed them tremendously\".\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h4>Jetset Travel</h4>\r\n<blockquote>\"I personally have completed many courses both overseas and in Australia throughout my career. After the first day of my Sales Management training, I went home so excited that finally I was at the beginning of an innovative and constructive training course. A course I felt that was going to provide me with confidence, not only in my professional career journey but also making me conscious of my attitude in general. As the course progressed, I constantly set my goals higher. And achieved them.\"</blockquote>\r\n<h4>Franchise Owner – Australia</h4>\r\n','Results','','publish','open','open','','results','','','2012-07-14 14:28:01','2012-07-14 21:28:01','',0,'http://sd-trunk/?page_id=9',0,'page','',0),(10,1,'2012-07-08 14:20:50','2012-07-08 21:20:50','','Posts','','inherit','open','open','','9-revision','','','2012-07-08 14:20:50','2012-07-08 21:20:50','',9,'http://sd-trunk/9-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(12,1,'2012-07-08 14:34:39','2012-07-08 21:34:39','This is just a sample post to go in Category 1','Sample Category 1 Post','','publish','open','open','','sample-category-1-post','','','2012-07-08 17:46:23','2012-07-09 00:46:23','',0,'http://sd-trunk/?p=12',0,'post','',0),(13,1,'2012-07-08 14:34:24','2012-07-08 21:34:24','','Sample Category 1 Post','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision','','','2012-07-08 14:34:24','2012-07-08 21:34:24','',12,'http://sd-trunk/12-revision/',0,'r