k, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n...or something like this:\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickies to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://sd-trunk/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-2','','','2012-07-08 13:13:05','2012-07-08 20:13:05','',2,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/2012/07/08/2-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(36,1,'2012-07-11 21:11:54','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2012-07-11 21:11:54','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/?p=36',0,'post','',0),(37,1,'2012-07-11 21:12:52','2012-07-12 04:12:52','','Events','','publish','open','open','','events','','','2012-07-14 15:34:45','2012-07-14 22:34:45','',0,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/?page_id=37',0,'page','',0),(38,1,'2012-07-11 21:12:09','2012-07-12 04:12:09','','Auto Draft','','inherit','open','open','','37-revision','','','2012-07-11 21:12:09','2012-07-12 04:12:09','',37,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/2012/07/11/37-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(39,1,'2012-07-11 21:13:31','2012-07-12 04:13:31',' ','','','publish','open','open','','39','','','2012-07-14 14:09:43','2012-07-14 21:09:43','',0,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/?p=39',12,'nav_menu_item','',0),(40,1,'2012-07-11 21:13:56','2012-07-12 04:13:56','<h3>Your Needs...</h3>\r\n<p>Quantum Strategies will assist your company by providing Needs Analyses, Research Interviews, Focus Groups and Culture Change Programs. QS know the keys to develop effective organisations that align leadership, strategy and culture to forge the company ahead with change that brings significant and lasting transformation.</p>\r\n<h3>Innovating Solutions...</h3>\r\n<p>Quantum Strategies’ goal is to bring economically efficient solutions that meet your companies pressing current need and to also provide long term solutions. QS offers a \'partnership\' approach to understanding and interpreting your company\'s needs which in turn enables us to supply our innovative solutions to each problem and challenge.</p>\r\n<h3>Implementation...</h3>\r\n<p>After the identification and analysis interpretation of your company\'s needs, Quantum Strategies provide the process of implementation. QS have a commitment to excellence that ensures this process offers your company ‘tried and true’ techniques that lead to positive and lasting change and dynamic outcomes for your company.</p>','Strategic Consulting','','publish','open','open','','strategic-consulting','','','2012-07-14 16:20:12','2012-07-14 23:20:12','',0,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/?page_id=40',0,'page','',0),(41,1,'2012-07-11 21:13:47','2012-07-12 04:13:47','','Auto Draft','','inherit','open','open','','40-revision','','','2012-07-11 21:13:47','2012-07-12 04:13:47','',40,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/2012/07/11/40-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(42,1,'2012-07-11 21:14:04','2012-07-12 04:14:04','<div class=\"emphasis\">\r\n<p>Quantum Strategies professional development ‘core value’ is to provide exceptional Training and Learning Development Programs that produce immediate and significant results for your company and its workforce. QS specialises in customised programs that range from Leadership and Management, Team Development Programs to Dynamic Sales and Coaching Training Programs.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Training...</h3>\r\n<p>Quantum Strategies provide skilled and competent training techniques using the latest facilitation methods to ensure the greatest transference and retention of new skills. QS has had years of successful implementation backing their training programs and continually see significant levels of increased performance as the result of new skill levels implemented in the work place.</p>\r\n<h3>Inspiration...</h3>\r\n<p>Quantum Strategies training programs are designed to inspire your company’s staff to apply their new skills at a practical level into their designated work assignment. The ‘hallmark’ of our facilitation process is our ability to competently adapt to the training needs of every group. Our training programs, workshops and activities ensure outcomes that are inspirational, results focused, pioneering and dynamic.</p>\r\n<h3>Motivation...</h3>\r\n<p>Quantum Strategies acknowledges that motivation is the key to improved performance. We also know that motivation ‘practice’ and theory are areas of challenge for any business. With our understanding and appreciation of employee motivation we create ‘key’ processes from advanced, solid and practical techniques to ensure that staff remain ‘self’ motivated in their work performance.</p>','Professional Development','','publish','open','open','','professional-development','','','2012-07-12 21:41:56','2012-07-13 04:41:56','',0,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/?page_id=42',0,'page','',0),(43,1,'2012-07-11 21:13:58','2012-07-12 04:13:58','','Auto Draft','','inherit','open','open','','42-revision','','','2012-07-11 21:13:58','2012-07-12 04:13:58','',42,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/2012/07/11/42-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(44,1,'2012-07-11 21:14:16','2012-07-12 04:14:16','<div class=\"emphasis\">\r\n<p>Alan Strudwick has over 32 years of Corporate Key Note Speaking.</p>\r\n<p>Alan is a dynamic Platform Speaker, Strategist, Facilitator, Educator and Trainer who competently brings his professional business acumen to the Speaker Platform. His unique \'people skill\' ability and advanced training techniques unlock the secrets to successful learning, independent of the size of his audience. Alan delivers his subject in an easy to grasp, lively way using vivid illustrations, demonstrations and real life examples. Alan is committed to delivering each and every subject he is invited to speak on with passion and excellence.</p>\r\n<p>The Aussie speaking Canadian now living in the USA provides a diversity of customized speaking topics to fit any company’s specific conference need.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<span><img class=\"align-right\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/keynote-image.png\" alt=\"\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"keynote-topics\">\r\n<h2>Specialized Topics</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Leadership</li>\r\n	<li>Negotiation</li>\r\n	<li>Purpose</li>\r\n	<li>Change</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Time Management</li>\r\n	<li>Sales and Customer Service</li>\r\n	<li>Motivation and Attitude</li>\r\n	<li>The Heart of Business</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Keynote Speaking','','publish','open','open','','keynote-speaking','','','2012-07-12 21:41:00','2012-07-13 04:41:00','',0,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/?page_id=44',0,'page','',0),(45,1,'2012-07-11 21:14:08','2012-07-12 04:14:08','','Auto Draft','','inherit','open','open','','44-revision','','','2012-07-11 21:14:08','2012-07-12 04:14:08','',44,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/2012/07/11/44-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(46,1,'2012-07-11 21:14:55','2012-07-12 04:14:55',' ','','','publish','open','open','','46','','','2012-07-14 14:09:42','2012-07-14 21:09:42','',0,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/?p=46',8,'nav_menu_item','',0),(47,1,'2012-07-11 21:14:55','2012-07-12 04:14:55',' ','','','publish','open','open','','47','','','2012-07-14 14:09:42','2012-07-14 21:09:42','',0,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/?p=47',7,'nav_menu_item','',0),(48,1,'2012-07-11 21:14:54','2012-07-12 04:14:54',' ','','','publish','open','open','','48','','','2012-07-14 14:09:42','2012-07-14 21:09:42','',0,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/?p=48',6,'nav_menu_item','',0),(49,1,'2012-07-08 14:50:17','2012-07-08 21:50:17','','Posts','','inherit','open','open','','9-revision-3','','','2012-07-08 14:50:17','2012-07-08 21:50:17','',9,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/2012/07/08/9-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(50,1,'2012-07-11 21:32:42','2012-07-12 04:32:42','','Pages','